71
00:03:41,795 --> 00:03:43,755
<c.bg_transparent>Baiklah, ini pertanyaannya!</c.bg_transparent>

72
00:03:43,839 --> 00:03:45,674
<c.bg_transparent>Apa yang harus kita lakukan dengannya?</c.bg_transparent>

73
00:03:48,510 --> 00:03:50,471
<c.bg_transparent>Meskipun dia wadah,</c.bg_transparent>

