106
00:05:32,197 --> 00:05:33,949
<c.bg_transparent>Para petinggi setuju.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:05:34,032 --> 00:05:37,494
<c.bg_transparent>Kau punya dua pilihan sekarang.</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:05:37,577 --> 00:05:39,454
