146
00:09:59,923 --> 00:10:02,342
<c.bg_transparent>Saat semua bagian Sukuna menghilang,</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:10:02,926 --> 00:10:04,636
<c.bg_transparent>akankah lebih sedikit orang</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:08,473
<c.bg_transparent>yang menderita karena kutukan?</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:10:10,267 --> 00:10:11,434
<c.bg_transparent>Tentu saja.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:10:19,526 --> 00:10:21,653
<c.bg_transparent>Kau masih memiliki jari itu?</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:10:26,366 --> 00:10:29,786
<c.bg_transparent>Setelah kulihat, ini menjijikkan.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:10:37,377 --> 00:10:40,922
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ini yang kedua, jadi, sepersepuluh.</i></c.bg_transparent>

153
00:10:41,006 --> 00:10:42,674
<c.bg_transparent><i>Apa yang akan terjadi?</i></c.bg_transparent>

154
00:10:50,849 --> 00:10:52,058
<c.bg_transparent>NAMA SEKULER</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:11:03,445 --> 00:11:06,781
<c.bg_transparent>Rasanya sangat tidak enak hingga aneh.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:11:07,282 --> 00:11:09,034
<c.bg_transparent><i>Aku yakin sekarang.</i></c.bg_transparent>

157
00:11:09,117 --> 00:11:10,660
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ini bukan hanya ketahanan fisik,</i></c.bg_transparent>

158
00:11:10,744 --> 00:11:13,580
<c.bg_transparent><i>dia bahkan mempertahankan kesadarannya
