159
00:11:14,164 --> 00:11:16,833
<c.bg_transparent><i>Dia genius yang sangat langka.</i></c.bg_transparent>

160
00:11:17,459 --> 00:11:18,585
<c.bg_transparent>Ada apa?</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:11:18,668 --> 00:11:20,670
<c.bg_transparent>Tak ada.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:11:20,754 --> 00:11:24,758
<c.bg_transparent>Boleh kuanggap kau siap untuk ini?</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:11:26,343 --> 00:11:27,594
<c.bg_transparent>Sama sekali tidak.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:11:27,677 --> 00:11:30,764
<c.bg_transparent>Aku masih memikirkan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>kenapa aku akan dieksekusi.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:11:30,847 --> 00:11:34,017
<c.bg_transparent>Tapi aku tidak bisa</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mengabaikan kutukan itu.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:11:34,934 --> 00:11:37,854
<c.bg_transparent>Permintaan terakhir itu sangat merepotkan.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:11:39,731 --> 00:11:41,858
<c.bg_transparent>Aku akan memakan setiap bagian Sukuna.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:11:41,941 --> 00:11:44,152
<c.bg_transparent>Aku tak peduli yang terjadi setelahnya.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:11:44,235 --> 00:11:47,364
<c.bg_transparent>Aku ditakdirkan untuk mati, bukan?</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:11:47,447 --> 00:11:51,076
<c.bg_transparent>Bagus. Aku suka orang sepertimu.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:11:51,159 --> 00:11:53,578
<c.bg_transparent>Sepertinya hal menyenangkan menantimu.</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:11:53,662 --> 00:11:56,122
<c.bg_transparent>Kemasi barang-barangmu hari ini.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:11:56,206 --> 00:11:57,624
<c.bg_transparent>Kita mau ke mana?</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:11:58,124 --> 00:11:59,000
<c.bg_transparent>Tokyo.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:11:59,084 --> 00:12:01,378
<c.bg_transparent>Fushiguro! Kau tampak hebat!</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:12:01,461 --> 00:12:03,213
<c.bg_transparent>Menurutmu begitu setelah melihat ini?</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:12:03,296 --> 00:12:07,884
<c.bg_transparent>Kau akan pindah</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>ke sekolah Penyihir Jujutsu, tempatku.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:12:07,967 --> 00:12:09,135
<c.bg_transparent>Apa?</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:12:09,719 --> 00:12:13,640
<c.bg_transparent><i>SMA Jujutsu Prefektur Tokyo.</i></c.bg_transparent>

180
00:12:13,723 --> 00:12:15,183
<c.bg_transparent>Omong-omong…</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:12:15,266 --> 00:12:17,352
<c.bg_transparent>Kau murid kelas satu ketiga.</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:12:17,435 --> 00:12:18,728
<c.bg_transparent>Sedikit sekali muridnya!</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:12:27,153 --> 00:12:30,615
<c.bg_transparent>Aku pergi, Kakek.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:12:30,699 --> 00:12:33,243
<c.bg_transparent>MAKAM KELUARGA ITADORI</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:12:34,661 --> 00:12:38,581
<c.bg_transparent>Jauh sekali di pegunungan.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Ini benar-benar Tokyo?</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:12:38,665 --> 00:12:41,084
<c.bg_transparent>Bahkan pinggiran Tokyo tampak seperti ini.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:12:41,167 --> 00:12:42,460
<c.bg_transparent>Di mana Fushiguro?</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:12:42,544 --> 00:12:44,838
<c.bg_transparent><i>Lukanya baru saja diobati
oleh Penyihir Jujutsu,</i></c.bg_transparent>

189
00:12:44,921 --> 00:12:46,381
<c.bg_transparent><i>jadi, dia sedang tidur nyenyak.</i></c.bg_transparent>

190
00:12:47,090 --> 00:12:50,885
<c.bg_transparent><i>SMA Jujutsu Prefektur Tokyo.</i></c.bg_transparent>

191
00:12:50,969 --> 00:12:54,889
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ini salah satu dari dua institusi
pendidikan sihir di Jepang.</i></c.bg_transparent>

192
00:12:54,973 --> 00:12:58,435
<c.bg_transparent><i>Di permukaan,
dikenal sebagai sekolah keagamaan swasta.</i></c.bg_transparent>

193
00:12:59,561 --> 00:13:04,399
<c.bg_transparent><i>Banyak Penyihir Jujutsu memakai tempat ini
sebagai markas setelah lulus.</i></c.bg_transparent>

194
00:13:04,482 --> 00:13:07,861
<c.bg_transparent>Ini bukan hanya soal pendidikan,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tapi juga mediasi dan dukungan dalam misi.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:13:07,944 --> 00:13:09,946
<c.bg_transparent>Semacam landasan di dunia sihir.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:13:11,239 --> 00:13:14,784
<c.bg_transparent>Jadi, kau akan diwawancarai</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>oleh kepala sekolah nanti.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:13:14,868 --> 00:13:16,244
<c.bg_transparent>Kepala Sekolah?</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:13:16,327 --> 00:13:19,831
<c.bg_transparent>Pendaftaranmu akan ditolak jika gagal,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>jadi, lakukan yang terbaik.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:13:19,914 --> 00:13:20,915
<c.bg_transparent>Apa?</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:13:20,999 --> 00:13:23,293
<c.bg_transparent>Jika begitu,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>apa aku akan langsung dieksekusi?</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:13:23,376 --> 00:13:27,172
<c.bg_transparent>Apa? Bukankah kau Pak Kepala?</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:13:28,423 --> 00:13:31,968
<c.bg_transparent>Hierarki apa pun</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>selain kekuatan membosankan.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:13:33,136 --> 00:13:35,722
<c.bg_transparent>Maaf, Pak Gojo. Terkadang dia muncul.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:13:35,805 --> 00:13:38,475
<c.bg_transparent>Tubuhmu semakin menarik.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:13:38,558 --> 00:13:41,060
<c.bg_transparent>- Aku masih berutang kepadamu.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Hei, jangan lagi!</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:13:41,144 --> 00:13:45,440
<c.bg_transparent>Begitu mengambil alih tubuh anak ini,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>aku akan membunuhmu lebih dahulu.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:13:45,940 --> 00:13:48,943
<c.bg_transparent>Suatu kehormatan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>bisa menjadi target Sukuna.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:13:49,569 --> 00:13:51,362
<c.bg_transparent>Apa dia terkenal?</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:13:51,946 --> 00:13:53,239
<c.bg_transparent>Ryomen Sukuna.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:13:53,323 --> 00:13:57,243
<c.bg_transparent>Dia makhluk gaib</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dengan empat tangan dan dua wajah.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:13:57,327 --> 00:14:00,079
<c.bg_transparent>Tapi dia pernah menjadi manusia sungguhan.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:14:00,163 --> 00:14:02,707
<c.bg_transparent>Hanya saja itu terjadi</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>lebih dari seribu tahun yang lalu.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:14:03,541 --> 00:14:05,376
<c.bg_transparent>Saat ilmu sihir berkembang,</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:14:05,460 --> 00:14:07,879
<c.bg_transparent><i>para Penyihir Jujutsu berkumpul
untuk menantangnya,</i></c.bg_transparent>

215
00:14:07,962 --> 00:14:09,422
<c.bg_transparent><i>tapi mereka gagal total.</i></c.bg_transparent>

216
00:14:09,923 --> 00:14:14,385
<c.bg_transparent><i>Dia dikenal sebagai Ryomen Sukuna dan kami
bahkan tak bisa menghancurkan adiposera</i></c.bg_transparent>

217
00:14:14,469 --> 00:14:17,096
<c.bg_transparent><i>yang diwariskan setelah kematiannya
sebagai benda kutukan.</i></c.bg_transparent>

218
00:14:17,764 --> 00:14:20,058
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tidak diragukan lagi, dia raja kutukan.</i></c.bg_transparent>

219
00:14:21,392 --> 00:14:23,186
<c.bg_transparent>Siapa yang lebih kuat, dia atau kau?</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:14:23,269 --> 00:14:25,313
<c.bg_transparent>Begini…</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:14:25,396 --> 00:14:29,567
<c.bg_transparent>Jika Sukuna mendapatkan semua kekuatannya,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>agak sulit menghadapinya.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:14:30,068 --> 00:14:31,152
<c.bg_transparent>Kau akan kalah?</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:14:32,237 --> 00:14:33,488
<c.bg_transparent>Aku akan menang.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:14:41,579 --> 00:14:43,540
<c.bg_transparent>- Satoru, kau terlambat!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Apa?</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:14:43,623 --> 00:14:45,542
<c.bg_transparent>Kau terlambat delapan menit.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:14:46,626 --> 00:14:48,795
<c.bg_transparent>Tidak cukup untuk menghukummu,</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:14:48,878 --> 00:14:52,507
<c.bg_transparent>tapi aku ingat menyuruhmu</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>memperbaiki keterlambatanmu.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:14:52,590 --> 00:14:55,677
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ada pria tua yang membuat boneka imut!</i></c.bg_transparent>

229
00:14:55,760 --> 00:14:59,097
<c.bg_transparent>Jika itu tidak cukup untuk menghukumku,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>maka tolong jangan lakukan itu.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:14:59,180 --> 00:15:03,309
<c.bg_transparent>Lagi pula, kau hanya membuat boneka.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Tidak bisakah menunggu delapan menit?</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:15:04,018 --> 00:15:05,895
<c.bg_transparent>Dia Kepala Sekolah, Pak Masamichi Yaga.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:15:06,604 --> 00:15:08,106
<c.bg_transparent>Apa itu dia?</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:15:08,189 --> 00:15:09,649
<c.bg_transparent>Namaku Yuji Itadori!</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:15:09,732 --> 00:15:11,651
<c.bg_transparent>Aku suka wanita seperti Jennifer Lawrence.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:15:11,734 --> 00:15:13,945
<c.bg_transparent>- Senang bertemu denganmu!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Kenapa kau di sini?</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:15:16,322 --> 00:15:17,157
<c.bg_transparent>Untuk wawancara.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:19,242
<c.bg_transparent>Aku bertanya kenapa kau di SMA Jujutsu?</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:15:20,076 --> 00:15:21,744
<c.bg_transparent>Untuk mempelajari kutukan?</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:15:21,828 --> 00:15:23,454
<c.bg_transparent>Maksudku setelah itu.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:15:23,955 --> 00:15:27,292
<c.bg_transparent>Setelah mempelajari kutukan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dan punya kekuatan untuk mengusirnya,</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:15:27,375 --> 00:15:29,919
<c.bg_transparent>apa yang akan kau lakukan?</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:15:30,461 --> 00:15:32,213
<c.bg_transparent>Kau bertanya kenapa…</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:15:33,256 --> 00:15:35,550
<c.bg_transparent>Aku ingin mengambil kembali jari Sukuna.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:15:35,633 --> 00:15:37,552
<c.bg_transparent>Berbahaya jika dibiarkan.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:15:37,635 --> 00:15:38,803
<c.bg_transparent>Kenapa?</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:15:40,388 --> 00:15:42,640
<c.bg_transparent>Kejahatan, kecelakaan, dan penyakit.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:15:42,724 --> 00:15:47,270
<c.bg_transparent>Wajar mendengar orang</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>yang tidak kau kenal mati setiap hari.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:15:47,353 --> 00:15:48,897
<c.bg_transparent>Sudah mulai.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:15:48,980 --> 00:15:53,234
<c.bg_transparent>Jadi, jika berkaitan dengan kutukan,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>kau merasa perlu ikut campur?</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:15:53,318 --> 00:15:55,570
<c.bg_transparent>Itu permintaan terakhir seseorang.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:15:55,653 --> 00:15:57,739
<c.bg_transparent>Siapa yang peduli detailnya?</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:15:57,822 --> 00:15:59,741
<c.bg_transparent>Aku hanya ingin menyelamatkan orang.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:15:59,824 --> 00:16:01,701
<c.bg_transparent>Permintaan terakhir?</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:16:02,327 --> 00:16:06,956
<c.bg_transparent>Jadi, kau akan melawan kutukan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hanya karena ada yang menyuruhmu?</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:16:07,832 --> 00:16:09,459
<c.bg_transparent>Kau gagal!</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:16:14,881 --> 00:16:17,842
<c.bg_transparent>Itu bukan boneka?</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:16:17,926 --> 00:16:20,720
<c.bg_transparent>Mayat Kutukan. Ini adalah boneka</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:16:20,803 --> 00:16:23,848
<c.bg_transparent>dengan kutukanku di dalamnya!</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:16:29,270 --> 00:16:30,813
<c.bg_transparent><i>Pukulan yang keras!</i></c.bg_transparent>

260
00:16:33,650 --> 00:16:35,485
<c.bg_transparent>Apa itu sungguh boneka?</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:16:37,028 --> 00:16:40,281
<c.bg_transparent>Sifat asli manusia muncul saat putus asa.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:16:40,990 --> 00:16:44,869
<c.bg_transparent>Aku akan terus menyerangmu</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sampai mendengar jawaban yang kumau.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:16:44,953 --> 00:16:48,748
<c.bg_transparent>Pertama, itu bukan permintaan terakhir</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sembarang orang.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:16:48,831 --> 00:16:52,210
<c.bg_transparent>Itu berasal dari anggota keluargaku!</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:17:01,177 --> 00:17:02,679
<c.bg_transparent>Sial, di mana?</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:17:08,351 --> 00:17:09,519
<c.bg_transparent>Astaga.</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:17:09,602 --> 00:17:12,272
<c.bg_transparent>Bahkan anggota keluarga</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dianggap sebagai "orang lain."</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:17:18,653 --> 00:17:22,782
<c.bg_transparent><i>Benar, itu boneka.
Tidak terluka atau takut.</i></c.bg_transparent>

269
00:17:22,865 --> 00:17:25,743
<c.bg_transparent>Penyihir Jujutsu selalu berhadapan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dengan kematian.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:17:25,827 --> 00:17:27,453
<c.bg_transparent>Bukan hanya kematian sendiri.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:17:27,537 --> 00:17:30,456
<c.bg_transparent>Ada saatnya kau harus</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mengoyak daging kutukan</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:17:30,540 --> 00:17:33,209
<c.bg_transparent>selagi menyaksikan kematian seseorang.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:17:34,002 --> 00:17:35,628
<c.bg_transparent>Itu pekerjaan tidak menyenangkan.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:17:35,712 --> 00:17:40,133
<c.bg_transparent>Itu membutuhkan sedikit kegilaan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dan motivasi tinggi.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:17:40,216 --> 00:17:42,593
<c.bg_transparent>Dan kau melakukannya</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>karena ada yang menyuruhmu?</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:17:42,677 --> 00:17:44,012
<c.bg_transparent>Yang benar saja!</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:17:44,637 --> 00:17:48,308
<c.bg_transparent>Aku bisa mengerti jika kau bilang</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>ingin menunda hukuman matimu.</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:17:48,391 --> 00:17:50,643
<c.bg_transparent>- Kau bercanda? Aku…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Aku mau tanya.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:17:50,727 --> 00:17:53,062
<c.bg_transparent>Jika kau mati karena kutukan,</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:17:53,146 --> 00:17:55,440
<c.bg_transparent>apa kau akan menyalahkan kakekmu?</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:17:57,984 --> 00:17:59,360
<c.bg_transparent>Kau…</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:17:59,444 --> 00:18:01,821
<c.bg_transparent>Kata-katamu kasar sekali.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:18:01,904 --> 00:18:04,324
<c.bg_transparent>Pendidikan adalah tentang</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>menusuk bagian yang sakit.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:18:05,074 --> 00:18:07,660
<c.bg_transparent>Kurasa…</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:18:15,168 --> 00:18:19,005
<c.bg_transparent>Aku tidak tahu apa yang kau pikirkan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>saat hampir mati.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:18:19,714 --> 00:18:22,342
<c.bg_transparent>Tapi aku yakin soal ini.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:18:22,842 --> 00:18:27,221
<c.bg_transparent>Jika ini berlanjut, kau mungkin akan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mengutuk kakek tercintamu nanti.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:18:27,722 --> 00:18:30,475
<c.bg_transparent>Tidak ada Penyihir Jujutsu</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>yang bisa mati tanpa penyesalan.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:18:30,975 --> 00:18:32,727
<c.bg_transparent>Aku akan tanya sekali lagi,</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:18:32,810 --> 00:18:36,773
<c.bg_transparent>kenapa kau datang ke SMA Jujutsu?</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:18:38,066 --> 00:18:42,153
<c.bg_transparent><i>Sejak kecil, aku sudah pandai
berolahraga dan berkelahi.</i></c.bg_transparent>

292
00:18:42,904 --> 00:18:47,575
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tapi aku tidak pernah merasa
hanya aku yang bisa melakukan itu.</i></c.bg_transparent>

293
00:18:53,748 --> 00:18:57,377
<c.bg_transparent>Hanya aku yang bisa memakan Sukuna.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:18:57,460 --> 00:18:59,712
<c.bg_transparent>Bahkan jika aku bisa</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>menghindari hukuman mati…</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:18:59,796 --> 00:19:01,839
<c.bg_transparent>Jika aku lari dari tugasku,</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:19:02,465 --> 00:19:06,594
<c.bg_transparent><i>aku akan makan, mandi, dan membaca komik.</i></c.bg_transparent>

297
00:19:07,804 --> 00:19:10,014
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tapi saat aku melamun…</i></c.bg_transparent>

298
00:19:11,724 --> 00:19:16,604
<c.bg_transparent><i>Aku sedih memikirkan seseorang
yang mati karena Sukuna.</i></c.bg_transparent>

299
00:19:16,687 --> 00:19:20,066
<c.bg_transparent><i>Apa aku harus meyakinkan diriku
bahwa itu bukan urusanku</i></c.bg_transparent>

300
00:19:20,149 --> 00:19:22,318
<c.bg_transparent><i>dan itu bukan salahku?</i></c.bg_transparent>

301
00:19:24,404 --> 00:19:26,697
<c.bg_transparent>Aku tidak mau!</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:19:27,407 --> 00:19:29,951
<c.bg_transparent>Entah apa yang akan terjadi saat aku mati,</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:19:30,034 --> 00:19:32,537
<c.bg_transparent>tapi aku tidak ingin menyesali hidupku.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:19:35,832 --> 00:19:38,960
<c.bg_transparent>Satoru, bawa dia ke asrama.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:19:39,043 --> 00:19:42,296
<c.bg_transparent>Selain itu, jelaskan semua</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tindakan keamanan kepadanya.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:19:42,380 --> 00:19:43,464
<c.bg_transparent>Apa?</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:19:44,799 --> 00:19:46,259
<c.bg_transparent>Kau lulus.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:19:46,342 --> 00:19:48,428
<c.bg_transparent>Selamat datang di SMA Jujutsu.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:19:53,182 --> 00:19:57,061
<c.bg_transparent>Maafkan aku. Aku lupa menghentikannya.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:19:58,396 --> 00:20:01,566
<c.bg_transparent>Hebat! Luas sekali!</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:20:01,649 --> 00:20:03,901
<c.bg_transparent>Murid kelas dua dan tiga</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sedang pergi sekarang.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:20:03,985 --> 00:20:06,446
<c.bg_transparent>- Halo! Ada orang di sini?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Tapi kita akan bertemu.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:20:06,529 --> 00:20:08,114
<c.bg_transparent>Lagi pula, tidak ada banyak orang.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:20:08,197 --> 00:20:11,742
<c.bg_transparent>Tapi kau tak perlu bertarung.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:20:11,826 --> 00:20:14,537
<c.bg_transparent>Fushiguro dan aku</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>yang akan menemukan jari-jari Sukuna.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:20:14,620 --> 00:20:16,914
<c.bg_transparent>Kau hanya perlu menunggu di sini.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:20:16,998 --> 00:20:19,167
<c.bg_transparent>Tidak. Aku sudah janji,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>jadi, akan kulakukan.</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:20:20,209 --> 00:20:22,253
<c.bg_transparent><i>Akan aneh jika aku bermalas-malasan</i></c.bg_transparent>

319
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:24,005
<c.bg_transparent>Kerja bagus.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:20:24,589 --> 00:20:28,092
<c.bg_transparent><i>sambil menunggu Fushiguro
memberiku jari setelah dihajar.</i></c.bg_transparent>

321
00:20:28,176 --> 00:20:29,552
<c.bg_transparent><i>Kau benar.</i></c.bg_transparent>

322
00:20:30,052 --> 00:20:34,390
<c.bg_transparent>Tapi mustahil kau tak akan terlibat</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dalam pertarungan.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:20:34,474 --> 00:20:36,559
<c.bg_transparent>Hei! Kau mengujiku?</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:20:37,643 --> 00:20:42,565
<c.bg_transparent>Jika semudah itu,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>kita pasti sudah menemukan semuanya.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:20:43,149 --> 00:20:49,572
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ada yang punya aura kuat,
ada yang tenang dan dirasuki roh.</i></c.bg_transparent>

326
00:20:50,156 --> 00:20:54,827
<c.bg_transparent>Mencari mereka sangat merepotkan.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:20:54,911 --> 00:20:56,954
<c.bg_transparent>Tapi kini ada kau.</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:20:57,038 --> 00:20:59,957
<c.bg_transparent>Sukuna dalam dirimu</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>akan memberi tahu keberadaan mereka</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:21:00,041 --> 00:21:02,376
<c.bg_transparent>karena dia ingin mendapatkan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>kekuatannya kembali.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:21:03,044 --> 00:21:05,546
<c.bg_transparent><i>Kalian berdua adalah wadah dan detektor,</i></c.bg_transparent>

331
00:21:05,630 --> 00:21:07,340
<c.bg_transparent><i>dan itu membuatmu menjadi radar.</i></c.bg_transparent>

332
00:21:07,423 --> 00:21:10,426
<c.bg_transparent>Jadi, tidak akan berhasil</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>jika kau tidak di lapangan dengan kami.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:21:10,510 --> 00:21:13,137
<c.bg_transparent>Menurutmu dia pria baik?</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:21:13,804 --> 00:21:16,807
<c.bg_transparent>Mungkin kau bisa membangun</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hubungan saling menguntungkan dengannya.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:21:16,891 --> 00:21:20,186
<c.bg_transparent>- Kau di sebelah.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Fushiguro!</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:21:20,269 --> 00:21:22,271
<c.bg_transparent>Kali ini kau tampak jauh lebih baik.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:21:22,355 --> 00:21:24,524
<c.bg_transparent>Ada banyak kamar kosong.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:21:24,607 --> 00:21:26,943
<c.bg_transparent>Bukankah lebih baik</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>jika tempat ini lebih ramai?</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:21:27,026 --> 00:21:29,862
<c.bg_transparent>- Kurasa bagus…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Kelas dan misi saja sudah cukup.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:21:29,946 --> 00:21:30,905
<c.bg_transparent>Merepotkan sekali…</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:21:30,988 --> 00:21:33,741
<c.bg_transparent>Hebat! Kamarmu tampak sangat rapi!</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:21:33,824 --> 00:21:37,370
<c.bg_transparent>- Seperti kataku, kau merepotkan!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Astaga!</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:21:37,453 --> 00:21:39,539
<c.bg_transparent>Tapi bukankah ini bagus?</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:21:39,622 --> 00:21:41,832
<c.bg_transparent>Kita akan pergi besok!</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:21:41,916 --> 00:21:45,836
<c.bg_transparent>Kita akan bertemu murid kelas tiga.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:21:45,920 --> 00:21:48,339
<c.bg_transparent>STASIUN MORIOKA</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:21:48,422 --> 00:21:55,137
<c.bg_transparent><i>Kereta ke Tokyo telah tiba.
Silakan berdiri di belakang garis kuning.</i></c.bg_transparent>

348
00:21:58,224 --> 00:22:00,935
<c.bg_transparent>Butuh empat jam untuk mencapai Morioka.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:22:01,018 --> 00:22:04,105
<c.bg_transparent>Akhirnya tiba saatnya berpamitan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dengan para orang bodoh itu!</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:22:07,567 --> 00:22:09,777
<c.bg_transparent>Aku akan tiba di Tokyo sore ini.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:22:09,860 --> 00:22:11,904
<c.bg_transparent>Bagaimana jika aku ditemukan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>pencari bakat?</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:22:12,572 --> 00:22:14,115
<c.bg_transparent>Mungkin dari Stardust Promotion.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:23:52,171 --> 00:23:55,091
<c.bg_transparent>Terjemahan subtitle oleh Tisa Anggriani</c.bg_transparent>

